created a class to invert the swg color :
if you pass 1 it invert the color if you pass 0 it wil remain same 

he filter property in CSS is used to apply visual effects to an element.
It can be used to change the appearance of an element, such as inverting its colors, blurring it, or applying a drop shadow.


.invert{
    filter:invert(1)
}
